      "span_text": "To prepare a list of common situations requiring agility in the supply chain context, we conducted a research on situations mentioned in works on supply chain agility, supply chain risk papers and industrial reports. recognize that, due to the complexity of the manufacturing environment, an exhaustive general list could not be easily determined and every manufacturing system has his challenges, risks and opportunities that push to adopt agile capabilities."
